high_descs: walk over to the kitchen stove top
take the dirty sauce pan off of the stove top
bring the sauce pan over to the kitchen sink
place the sauce pan inside the sink and rinse it off, then pick it up again
take the sauce pan over to the kitchen stove
place the sauce pan on the same burner it was originally on
anns.task_desc: clean the sauce pan on the stove

high_descs: Pick up the the dirty pan from the lower right of the stove.
Bring the pan to the sink.
Clean the pan in the sink.
Bring the pan to the stove.
Put the pan on the lower right of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned pan on the lower right of the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and face the stove on your right.
Pick up the pan from the stove.
Turn right, then right again and face the sink on your left.
Place the pot in the sink, wash the pot, drain the water from the sink, and pick up the pot in the sink.
Turn left, then left again and face the stove on your right.
Place the pan on the stove in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean pan on the stove.
